              "name": "Player Core",
              "page": 455,
              "type": "source"
            }
          ],
          "text": "A creature with this trait is a member of the elf ancestry. Elves are mysterious people with rich traditions of magic and scholarship who typically have low-light vision. An ability with this trait can be used or selected only by elves. A weapon with this trait is created and used by elves.",
