            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The elementalist unleashes powerful static electricity in a 20-foot emanation that lasts for 1 minute. All squares in the area become hazardous terrain for other creatures. A creature takes 1 electricity damage each time it moves into one of these squares. While in the area, creatures take a \u20131 status penalty to saves against electricity spells.",
